---
description: Feature architecture rules
globs:
  - "src/features/**/*.ts"
  - "src/features/**/*.tsx"
alwaysApply: false
---

Feature rules:
- Keep each feature self-contained
- Co-locate hooks, schemas, types, and api helpers
- Prefer small hooks and focused modules
- Avoid unnecessary cross-feature coupling
- Shared code belongs in src/lib or src/components